@greeting
Elder: Welcome, traveler.
Elder: Our village has been troubled by slimes lately.
Elder: If you could help us, we would be grateful.

@quest
Elder: The slimes come from the forest to the east.
Elder: Be careful out there.
Hero: We'll handle it.

@thanks
Elder: You've done a great service for our village.
Elder: Please, take this as a token of our gratitude.
